# Magtrak no longer reads an API key from this file.
#
# Deadline extraction now runs through pi (the coding-agent SDK). Model
# credentials live in pi's own config, not here:
#
#   ~/.pi/agent/auth.json    — provider logins (Anthropic, Google Gemini, ...)
#   ~/.pi/agent/models.json  — local models (e.g. Ollama qwen2.5:7b)
#
# Set those up with `pi` (run `/login` in interactive mode) and `ollama pull`.
# See README.md "How It Works".
#
# This file is kept only so older tooling that sources a .env doesn't complain.
